{"tid":1472942,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實應該同傅國豪道歉","createTime":"2019-08-14T17:03:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T18:21:25.000Z","uid":258534,"like":3,"dislike":83,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"f1627abdb64e582dc76059b578884acc5520087f","tid":1472942,"uid":258534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:03:00.000Z","msg":"宜家好多人拎住呢個point黎鬧示威者暴力，無人性。其實係人權角度，就算佢係臥底、係武警、係鬼都好，都真係唔應該打佢，特別係我地嘅立場係爭取緊<span style=\"color: red;\">民主人權</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住，我地係要做俾全世界，做俾國際睇。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n係公開場合，例如民間記者會道歉，最好可以眾籌支付佢嘅醫藥費，<br />\n1. 可以表現我地同警察嘅唔同，做錯係會認<br />\n2. 表現番我地和理非一面<br />\n3. 拎番淺黃支持度，好多淺黃因爲呢排太多衝突暴力，開始有反對唔認同嘅聲音<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果真係道歉 + 眾籌，一定要做好文宣，話俾全世界，包括藍絲知，唔好俾藍絲假新聞拎左個光環！等陣變左藍絲捐錢，反曱甴暴力，就on99白做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n同埋，勇武真係要停一停<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />包括圍警局、佔馬路、不合作等運動，宜家真心全世界淨係focus曬係暴力衝突同民生破壞，唔記得曬一開始100萬200萬係幾咁和平<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />818最好係文宣時加上行完即散、真和理非等字眼，吸引番和理非d人出黎。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求下大家和理非唔好再講講就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要真係做到俾人睇。唔好再好似之前7區集會咁，宣傳和理非，但變左圍警局、衝突。</span></span> 好彩香港人係善忘，只要我地做番好，暴力就會慢慢淡化。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實身邊好多藍絲，由一開始話d人遊行係搞亂香港外國勢力，宜家變左話我唔反對d人遊行，但暴力打警察就係唔啱lol</span></span> 所以勇武嘅大家，辛苦曬你地，請你地休息下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實不斷嘅警民衝突，警察的確會越黎越多失誤，越黎越多pointa 俾我地鬧。但相對地，跳出同溫層，我地都一樣，有越黎越多失誤俾對家捉住，例如今次機場事件。<br />\n<br />\n其實件事黎到今日，我諗每一個人都感受到，個性質已經同一開始唔同，焦點亦都越黎越模糊，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係咪時候要改變策略？</span></span>"},{"pid":"59d49f5c0ca2b28ff92756e9987330c57e8a5633","tid":1472942,"uid":5499,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:03:59.000Z","msg":"道你老母"},{"pid":"92c1f557ded3a1aa451292a8e3c10cb3c80f5300","tid":1472942,"uid":73381,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:04:28.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"b3ebb75d1a479d2d453d986d6b435c547097e631","tid":1472942,"uid":228436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:05:41.000Z","msg":"其實我地示威嘅目的都係五大訴求<br />\n依家一樣都未達成<br />\n可唔可以唔好講其他野住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#beHUMBLE"},{"pid":"fe1380f932b5ebaa59a09695eb7d72050ed1bd9d","tid":1472942,"uid":12773,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:06:43.000Z","msg":"樓主垃圾死全家"},{"pid":"3c5b0459ce53b32acb50d5286511d4b50dfd4190","tid":1472942,"uid":202256,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:06:47.000Z","msg":"道佢老味<br />\n佢自己叫人打佢<br />\n都仲未叫佢講多謝<br />\n<br />\n受阻旅客就話要心表遺憾"},{"pid":"e650d58a4c0275492c3a0b53d8cc9b6f801c2e00","tid":1472942,"uid":170589,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:08:37.000Z","msg":"道歉已經on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要眾籌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b981a14f264d2338ebdd510a09817ce2257b97","tid":1472942,"uid":149751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:08:52.000Z","msg":"你好撚on 9"},{"pid":"88604018e0899cc6ae190ff2f8d4c0de3eaf12c7","tid":1472942,"uid":92088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:10:01.000Z","msg":"道你老母"},{"pid":"6382e0d2215557d2f0ff4afe501e430df6fa7305","tid":1472942,"uid":46325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:10:28.000Z","msg":"唔好戇鳩 賠錢被極權打手為乜，根本就道歉都唔應該。當晚無的佢出來，隨時唔知會有幾多個人遭殃<br />\n<br />\n退一百萬步，就算真係有咩野要道歉賠償，一切等有普選之後再講"},{"pid":"38906d230a47519684171e6c6505b6ed1cf6e8f8","tid":1472942,"uid":12441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:11:01.000Z","msg":"佢自己話想比人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdae633430bf2ade93268d2023e9ec5c6810d7d","tid":1472942,"uid":46325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:12:07.000Z","msg":"咁撚戇鳩唔怪得要開個p牌出來講，咁撚笨七嘅野都講得出真係唔怕俾人cap 圖落來笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94029bf0b3e73856caca4b8dc24862c33c1131df","tid":1472942,"uid":295889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:13:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">【公投】民間記者會設限825通牒林奠答應訴求（係答應唔係回應！！！）</span></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1472905\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1472905</a>"},{"pid":"e8fad917273878678840132967956f245fc3db22","tid":1472942,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d9b981a14f264d2338ebdd510a09817ce2257b97","tid":1472942,"uid":149751,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:08:52.000Z","msg":"你好撚on 9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:14:00.000Z","msg":"你都係，請不推文回覆條撚樣"},{"pid":"f6575835d1c26ac4029f3b2102b18d5c23a21ad9","tid":1472942,"uid":21299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:16:43.000Z","msg":"傻咗？同佢道歉<br />\n又唔見林鄭，黑警，白衫出嚟同大家道歉？"},{"pid":"ae49d18561484dacdba415a793889f0442dcf623","tid":1472942,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T17:17:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反向思維，其實做得過<br />\n好多人唔明</span>"},{"pid":"3d4541b86f8a